From b50d677f1af2c52b492d89865e727294856daaa8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Amanda Van Syckle <amvansyckle@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 28 Mar 2026 08:44:13 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Strict design system overhaul: 8pt grid, Inter Tight
 headings, mobile optimization

Complete rewrite of globals.css with strict token system: 8 spacing
tokens on 8pt grid, Inter Tight for headings, pill-shaped buttons,
56px inputs, card components with hover/active states, 44px touch
targets. Refactored all pages and components to use tokens with zero
arbitrary values. Removed Supabase/API routes (not needed for static
MVP). Mobile-first responsive design throughout.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
